description: We present you with “Lady in a Footlocker,” starring Latex Lucy and Frank M. Standing in shiny clear leggings and ballet style heels right out of master 1950s fetish artist John Willie, the top half of Lucy’s form is actually INSIDE an old footlocker, and when Frank M., wearing a mask and suit, opens the locker’s top, we see Lucy within, wearing a form-fitting gray latex body suit and mask.
title: Lady In a Footlocker!
